text: The learning curve of the service provider is best embedded in the solutions it has developed. The learnings, experience are converted into expertise by service providers via solutions & accelerators. Solutions help  service providers deliver better and faster for a new customer.

text: What has the service provider learned from its prior work, and how it can help a new customer? This is best determined by the learning curve of the organization‚Äîthe ability to deliver better and faster because of its learning over the years.
